DPM_TEAM04

Class Resources

  • java.lang.Object
    • DPM_TEAM04.Resources

  • public class Resources
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all resources (Motors, Sensors, Filters, Display) and all constants required for operation. Resources are initialized once this class is loaded by the JVM Sensor data is also acquired through this class
    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Kareem Halabi, Alexis Giguere-Joannette, Tristan Toupin

      • getFrontUSData

        public static float getFrontUSData()
        Fetch data from the front ultrasonic sensor applying a median filter. It fetches a number of samples, sort the array of samples and returns the median value of the array.
        Returns:
        Returns the median value of the array of samples.

        Returns:
